name: DATA-2883 - building - ACX Table Profiling
description:
This profiling task is to analyze the 'building' table from Guidewire (ACX). DATA-2883 is an epic about the refactoring of the DataWarehouse at Andover, specifically about the design and development of the 'Risk' domain.
This analysis is conducted on 99k rows (0.8%) of the data available.
